00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,160
okay?

592
00:30:21,540 --> 00:30:23,400
How could I keep it a secret?

593
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:25,970
How could I keep...

594
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:30,770
I don't know how.

595
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:33,640
Don't cry.

596
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,480
Don't cry.

597
00:30:39,380 --> 00:30:40,850
No more beauty if you cry.

598
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:43,170
You're not cute anymore if you cry.

599
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:44,680
You're becoming ugly.

600
00:30:50,290 --> 00:30:50,740
[So]

601
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:53,520
[I'm only a fictional character
