602
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:54,900
[I don't actually exist]

603
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:56,800
[in this world.]

604
00:30:57,820 --> 00:30:59,440
[How about Hehuan Palace?]

605
00:30:59,580 --> 00:31:01,080
[How about Master?]

606
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:04,120
Because I

607
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:07,330
didn't have parents since little,

608
00:31:08,060 --> 00:31:09,900
so my Master

609
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:11,720
adopted me since then.

610
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:14,900
I've been staying in the Hehuan Palace

611
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:16,380
with him since little.

612
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,690
At least at that time,

613
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:23,160
I considered myself in a family.

614
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:28,260
[So everything about me]

615
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:30,080
[doesn't actually exist.]

616
00:31:57,980 --> 00:32:01,530
Xiao Wudi, are you home?

617
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:06,840
Tell me if you're in there.

618
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:09,330
I'm really worried about you.

619
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:39,200
Mother, I'm home.

620
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:40,440
You're back.

621
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,520
[No.]

622
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,250
[I still don't know]

623
00:32:50,250 --> 00:32:51,920
[how to face you.]

624
