I prepared seafood feast for you.

625
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:28,400
You ordered a cake?

626
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,620
It's so adorable.

627
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:32,220
It can just be our dessert.

628
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:34,320
This is not for you.

629
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,650
Who is it for then?

630
00:33:36,780 --> 00:33:38,690
Someone gave it to me.

631
00:33:38,690 --> 00:33:40,400
So I can't have it?

632
00:33:41,090 --> 00:33:42,000
No.

633
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:43,700
You can eat my stuff,

634
00:33:43,700 --> 00:33:44,100
why can't

635
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:45,530
I eat yours?

636
00:33:45,530 --> 00:33:47,850
Someone ordered me to keep it for him.

637
00:33:48,340 --> 00:33:49,920
You can't eat it as well?

638
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:54,440
Okay then, forget it.

639
00:33:58,660 --> 00:34:00,790
Wash your hands and let's have dinner.

640
00:34:04,460 --> 00:34:07,020
Mother, I'm not eating.

641
00:34:07,020 --> 00:34:08,420
I've already had my meal.

642
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:10,080
I want to go for a walk.

643
00:34:15,420 --> 00:34:17,320
What about the seafood feast?

644
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:35,880
Why is he not back yet?

645
00:34:37,699 --> 00:34:39,969
Will he take it too hard?

646
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:43,530
He won't.

647
00:34:43,659 --> 00:34:45,560
He's not that foolish.

648
00:34:47,659 --> 00:34:49,810
I can't look at you now.

649
00:34:53,659 --> 00:34:56,330
But we can't stay apart forever, right?

650
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:24,700
I'm sorry, miss.

651
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,200
I'm sorry, miss.

652
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:10,600
What are you looking at?

653
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:14,490
I'm not punishing her.

654
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:15,740
I just don't know

655
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:17,320
how to speak to her.

656
00:36:25,170 --> 00:36:26,850
What do you want me to do then?

657
00:36:26,850 --> 00:36:29,080
It's not her fault as well.

658
00:36:33,660 --> 00:36:34,680
Also,

659
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:36,180
I didn't ask her to

660
00:36:36,180 --> 00:36:37,360
wait me over there.

661
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:38,500
I told her

662
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,980
that I don't want to see her.

663
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:41,840
She insisted to stay there for me.

664
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,760
Can you blame me for it?

665
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,490
[What is she doing there?]

666
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:43,980
Doudou,

667
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:46,200
let's get back the mask from miss.

668
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:48,570
Miss, can you return

669
00:37:48,570 --> 00:37:49,580
his mask?

670
00:37:49,580 --> 00:37:50,800
Return me the mask.

671
00:37:52,620 --> 00:37:53,610
Can you

672
00:37:53,610 --> 00:37:55,460
lend it to me for a while longer?

673
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:56,370
No.

674
00:37:57,380 --> 00:37:58,900
Nan Xing,

675
00:37:58,900 --> 00:38:01,120
why are you wearing the mask?

676
00:38:03,140 --> 00:38:05,220
I... I'm waiting for someone.

677
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:07,100
Who would wait for someone this way?

678
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:08,500
I know, you're waiting for Tang Sanzang.

679
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:09,900
Sun Wukong waits for Tang Sanzang.

680
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:11,760
Who is Tang Sanzang?

681
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:14,100
Tang Sanzang is...

682
00:38:14,100 --> 00:38:16,000
Where is Tang Sanzang?

683
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:20,400
Master!

